snippet: Australian Treasurer Joe Hockey said on Thursday Russia would take part in the G20 Summit in Brisbane later this year, laying to rest questions Russia might be barred from attending over Moscow's annexation of the Ukrainian territory of Crimea....

headline.print_headline: Russia Will Be at G20, Ukraine to Be Discussed-Australian Treasurer
headline.main: Russia Will Be at G20, Ukraine to Be Discussed-Australian Treasurer

lead_paragraph: Australian Treasurer Joe Hockey said on Thursday Russia would take part in the G20 Summit in Brisbane later this year, laying to rest questions Russia might be barred from attending over Moscow's annexation of the Ukrainian territory of Crimea.
